{"type": "article", "id": 2954, "title": "回头看看微软十年前的智能手表", "description": "无线充电、可更换表盘、显示天气和好友消息。它的功能听上去并不过时。", "date": "2014-10-21T08:29:53Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 260, "name": "微软"}, {"id": 1233, "name": "智能手表"}, {"id": 28, "name": "可穿戴"}, {"id": 3652, "name": "SPOT"}], "category": 4, "column": null, "author": 3, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607155205o2lBw0uUmAsFWj7d.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">有报道称微软<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/display/articles/2938\" target=\"_blank\">将在未来几周发布智能手表</a>、功能听上去和 Moto 360、Apple Watch 差不多，唯一特色是它同时支持与 iOS、Android 和 Windows Phone 这三个平台的智能手机同步数据</span><span class=\"s1\" style=\"line-height:1.5;\">。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">不过其实早在</span><span class=\"s2\"> 2004 </span><span class=\"s1\">年，微软就曾经和 </span><span class=\"s2\">Fossil</span><span class=\"s1\">、西铁城、</span><span class=\"s2\">Suunto </span><span class=\"s1\">推出</span><span class=\"s2\"> SPOT </span><span class=\"s1\">手表。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s2\">SPOT </span><span class=\"s1\">手表可以说是业界最早的智能手表，它的功能和形态和现有的智能手表十分相似，Suunto 的版本甚至有看似圆形的液晶屏，<span class=\"s1\">价格从 </span><span class=\"s2\">120 </span><span class=\"s1\">美元到 </span><span class=\"s2\">300 </span><span class=\"s1\">美元不等</span>。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607155204g5xonbRt4QwVf3Dq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.25714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s2\">SPOT </span><span class=\"s1\">是“智能个人设备技术”的简写，能够将</span><span class=\"s1\">咖啡馆、天气预报以及闹钟显示在</span><span class=\"s1\">小屏幕上。当时智能手机并未普及，因此微软选择利用 </span><span class=\"s2\" style=\"line-height:1.5;\">FM </span><span class=\"s1\" style=\"line-height:1.5;\">无线广播频段传输信息。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\" style=\"line-height:1.5;\">信息首先被微软发送到无线基站，然后以广播方式发送到用户设备上 </span><span class=\"s2\" style=\"line-height:1.5;\">FM </span><span class=\"s1\" style=\"line-height:1.5;\">接收器。为了让 </span><span class=\"s2\" style=\"line-height:1.5;\">SPOT </span><span class=\"s1\" style=\"line-height:1.5;\">技术能够应用于各种场合，微软设计了成本非常低廉的、体积非常微小的承载 SPOT </span><span class=\"s1\" style=\"line-height:1.5;\">技术的芯片组，这个芯片组包括处理器、无线接收器和存储器。</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">当时 3G 刚刚起步，绝大多数地区都还是 2G 网络。事实上，晚三年推出的 iPhone 都没支持 3G。这大概也是微软</span><span class=\"s1\">选择</span><span class=\"s2\"> FM 推送信息的活动</span><span class=\"s1\">。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">花费</span><span class=\"s2\"> 59 </span><span class=\"s1\">或者</span><span class=\"s2\"> 99 </span><span class=\"s1\">美元，用户可以从信息广播服务 </span><span class=\"s2\">MSN Direct </span><span class=\"s1\">收听 </span><span class=\"s2\">12 </span><span class=\"s1\">个频道信息，包含体育、新闻、天气、股市等。</span><span class=\"s1\">在 </span><span class=\"s2\">FM </span><span class=\"s1\">调频波的帮助下，</span><span class=\"s2\">MSN </span><span class=\"s1\">上的好友也可以向 </span><span class=\"s2\">SPOT </span><span class=\"s1\">发送信息——但由于 FM 的原理，你没法回复。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">其它前瞻设计还包括可以更换表盘画面，以及无线充电功能。听起来和现在</span><span class=\"s2\"> Moto 360、Apple Watch </span><span class=\"s1\">是不是相当接近？</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">然而微软估计错了当时的市场环境，在移动宽带刚刚起步的情况下，微软当时只能依靠 </span><span class=\"s2\">FM </span><span class=\"s1\">调频波一种方式输送数据。很少人希望购买一款只接收 </span><span class=\"s2\">12 </span><span class=\"s1\">个频道有限数据的手表。用户对于可穿戴设备的需求甚至不如现在，而且还需要花费</span><span class=\"s2\"> 59 </span><span class=\"s1\">或</span><span class=\"s2\"> 99 </span><span class=\"s1\">美元的订阅费。最终微软在</span><span class=\"s2\"> 2008 </span><span class=\"s1\">年停止了对</span><span class=\"s2\"> SPOT </span><span class=\"s1\">平台的支持。</span> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}